name: Hasta el fin del mundo
description:
This is the beginning of a very special series for me. 
A correspondence through time and space and specially an imaginative union. Those will be pictures taken by my partner, who is currently faraway, for me to edit them. It's very beautiful when you see the world through each other's eyes. When he took the pictures he knew exactly what I would see in them and into what I would transform them later, in my way to reimagine the reality into something else, into what the world and nature may suggest, but has to be seen through a certain lens, that is now shared. 

pictures taken in Tierra del Fuego
edited by me
